<h1 property="name" id="wb-cont">Station Results - Historical Data</h1>
<!-- Page content -->
<p data-options='{"optLimit":"yearRange","year":2013,"month":6,"day":4}'>1079 stations found in Quebec, with data available between 1840 and 2017. Stations are listed in alphabetical order. Confirm the <a href="/glossary_e.html#dataInt">Data Interval</a> and the date for one of the stations listed and click "GO" to display the historical data.</p>
